ases while the other remains in the liquid\nstate. The non-ideal composition dependence of viscosity is anti-correlated\nwith average inherent structure energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2010 12:42:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-12-22"}
