thm. Numerical results are also\nprovided to gain insight into the impacts of the GTC and the error performance\nrequirement on the accessible capacity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2010 06:26:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Sep 2013 01:00:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Dec 2013 13:10:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-17"}
